nCOUNTERFEITERS<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">80th Academy Award \nNomination<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">Best Foreign Language \nFilm<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 6pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">starring<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">Karl \nMarkovics&nbsp;&nbsp; August Diehl&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Devid \nStriesow<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 4pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">written \n</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">and</SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"> directed \n</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">by</SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"> </SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">Stefan Ruzowitzky \n</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><B><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=5><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">Thursday, February 7, \n2007<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><B><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">6:30<B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"> </SPAN></B>p.m. \ncocktails<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">7:00<B><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold\"> </SPAN></B>p.m. screening&nbsp;&nbsp; 9:00 p.m. \ndinner<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<H1><B><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=4><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 13pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">SONY \nSCREENING ROOM</SPAN></FONT></B><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=4><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 13pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></H1>\n<H4><st1:Street w:st=\"on\"><st1:address \nstyle=\"BACKGROUND-POSITION: left bottom; BACKGROUND-IMAGE: url(res://ietag.dll/#34/#1001); BACKGROUND-REPEAT: repeat-x\" \ntabIndex=0 w:st=\"on\"><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">550 Madison \nAvenue</SPAN></FONT></st1:address></st1:Street><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\"><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">between</SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"> 55<SUP>th</SUP> \n</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">and</SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"> \n</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">56<SUP>th</SUP> \n</SPAN></FONT><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">Streets</SPAN></FONT><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=3><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></H4>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><B><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></B></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">peggy@peggysiegal.com or \n212-935-6700<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">this invitation is \nnon-transferable<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><FONT \nface=\"Century Gothic\" size=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" \nsize=1><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">The true \nstory of Salomon Sorowitsch, counterfeiter extraordinaire and bohemian. After \ngetting arrested and sent to a concentration camp in 1944, he agrees to help the \nNazis in an organized counterfeit operation set up to help finance the war \neffort.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" \nsize=1><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" \nsize=1><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\">It was the \nbiggest counterfeit money scam of all times. Over 130 million pound sterling \nwere printed, under conditions that couldn't have been more tragic or \nspectacular. During the last years of the war, as the German Reich saw that the \nend was near, the authorities decided to produce their own banknotes in the \ncurrencies of their major war enemies. They hoped to use the duds to flood the \nenemy economy and fill the empty war coffers. At the Sachsenhausen concentration \ncamp, two barracks were separated from the rest of the camp and the outside \nworld, and transformed into a fully equipped counterfeiter&#8217;s workshop. \n\"Operation Bernhard\" was born. Prisoners were brought to Sachsenhausen from \nother camps to implement the plan: professional printers, fastidious bank \nofficials and simple craftsmen all became members of the top-secret \ncounterfeiter commando. They had the choice: if they cooperated with the enemy, \nthey had a chance to survive, as first-class prisoners in a \"golden cage\" with \nenough to eat and a bed to sleep in. If they sabotaged the operation, a sure \ndeath awaited them. For THE COUNTERFEITERS, it was not only a question of saving \ntheir own lives, but also about saving their conscience as \nwell...<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Century Gothic\" size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Century Gothic'\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Arial size=2><SPAN \nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></FONT></P></DIV></BODY></HTML>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":4,"is_redacted":false}]